76}, {\"ngram\": \"student artists\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 304}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 26, the International Child Art Foundation - or ICAF - launched a worldwide Olympic-themed art competition for students aged 14-20.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Child Art Foundation\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 358}, {\"ngram\": \"ICAF\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 368}, {\"ngram\": \"a worldwide Olympic-themed art competition\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Titled #MyFavoriteSport, the campaign allows participants to create artwork inspired by their favorite sport for a chance to win a gold, silver or bronze medal along with a cash prize - $3,000 for gold, $2,000 for silver and $1,000 for bronze.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the campaign\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"participants\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 505}, {\"ngram\": \"artwork\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"their favorite sport\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze medal\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"a cash prize\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a $10 entry fee for artists who wish to participate.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a $10 entry fee\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"artists\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition, which will accept submissions until Sept. 30, will conclude Oct. 4 when the medal winners - based on votes cast by the public - will be announced.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"submissions\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"Sept.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal winners\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"votes\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ashfaq Ishaq, ICAF's founder, said he created the organization in 1997 to provide children with a platform to share their talent in a world that often prioritizes the work of professional, adult artists.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 927, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"score\": 0.9462158510720063, \"rank\": 0.056834480895920574, \"text\": \"Ishaq\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\"}, {\"begin\": 934, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ICAF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the organization\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 982}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"a platform\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"their talent\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"professional, adult artists\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"What we believe is that art produced by children is arguably the most honest form of human expression and creativity and yet, the world often ignores children's imaginations,\\\" Ishaq said.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1302, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"score\": 0.9462158510720063, \"rank\": 0.056834480895920574, \"text\": \"Ishaq\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"the most honest form\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"human expression\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"children's imaginations\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our goal is to encourage students to embrace and share their creativity with the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our goal\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1323}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1348}, {\"ngram\": \"their creativity\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1386}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This, Ishaq said, is how ICAF came to organize and host the world's largest school art program,The Arts Olympiad- an art competition that features artwork from students aged 8-12 in after-school programs and art studios, including those who are home-schooled from around the world.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"score\": 0.9462158510720063, \"rank\": 0.056834480895920574, \"text\": \"Ishaq\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\"}, {\"begin\": 1430, \"end\": 1434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ICAF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's largest school art program\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"The Arts Olympiad- an art competition\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1537}, {\"ngram\": \"artwork\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"art studios\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Arts Olympiad directly inspired the #MyFavoriteSport campaign, Ishaq said.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arts_Olympiad\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arts Olympiad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arts_Olympiad\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arts_Olympiad\"}, {\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"score\": 0.9462158510720063, \"rank\": 0.056834480895920574, \"text\": \"Ishaq\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the #MyFavoriteSport campaign\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is the Olympics, which is in its own way is a story about young people's passions and imaginations,\\\" Ishaq said.\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isaac\", \"score\": 0.9462158510720063, \"rank\": 0.05683448089592