7}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign's reach\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In recent weeks, I have focused on creating engaging content highlighting the contest's theme, prizes and submission guidelines,\\\" Yu said.\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3230, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recent weeks\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"engaging content\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3152}, {\"ngram\": \"the contest's theme\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"prizes\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"submission guidelines\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3219}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The experience has been enriching.\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3266, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The experience\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have gained valuable hands-on experience in social media marketing, and I have developed a deeper appreciation for the power of the arts and its impact on young people.\\\"\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"valuable hands-on experience\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3309}, {\"ngram\": \"social media marketing\", \"from\": 3313, \"to\": 3335}, {\"ngram\": \"a deeper appreciation\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3379}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3393}, {\"ngram\": \"the arts\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"its impact\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yu said she chose to become an intern at ICAF because she wanted to have the opportunity to contribute to the foundation's mission to support young artists.\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3481, \"end\": 3485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ICAF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_Co-belligerent_Air_Force\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yu\", \"from\": 3440, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"an intern\", \"from\": 3468, \"to\": 3477}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"the foundation's mission\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"young artists\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Supporting art in youth is crucial for multiple reasons,\\\" Yu said.\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3613}, {\"ngram\": \"youth\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple reasons\", \"from\": 3638, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"First, art fosters creativity, imagination and problem-solving skills essential for personal and academic growth.\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"First, art fosters creativity\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3696}, {\"ngram\": \"imagination\", \"from\": 3698, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"problem-solving skills\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3736}, {\"ngram\": \"personal and academic growth\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Second, art provides a powerful platform for self-expression, allowing young people to explore their emotions and perspectives.\", \"from\": 3781, \"to\": 3908, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3792}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful platform\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3821}, {\"ngram\": \"self-expression\", \"from\": 3826, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"their emotions\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"perspectives\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Third, art education can contribute to cultural understanding and appreciation, promoting diversity and inclusivity.\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 4025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"art education\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural understanding\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3970}, {\"ngram\": \"appreciation\", \"from\": 3975, \"to\": 3987}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 3999, \"to\": 4008}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 4013, \"to\": 4024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, involvement in the arts can boost self-confidence and build resilience, empowering young people to reach their full potential.\\\"\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"involvement\", \"from\": 4035, \"to\": 4046}, {\"ngram\": \"the arts\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4058}, {\"ngram\": \"self-confidence\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4084}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4105}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 4118, \"to\": 4130}, {\"ngram\": \"their full potential\", \"from\": 4140, \"to\": 4160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than these general benefits, Yu said art is important because of the distinct ability it has to influence everyone differently.\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these general benefits\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4196}, {\"ngram\": \"Yu\", \"from\": 4198, \"to\": 4200}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4209}, {\"ngram\": \"the distinct ability\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4254}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 4275, \"to\": 4283}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The traditional landscape arts did not grab my heart as a child.\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4363, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The traditional landscape arts\", \"from\": 4299, \"to\": 4329}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4351}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 4355, \"to\": 4362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, I was more into arts that represented fashio